    "help": {
      "topics": [
        {
          "id": "overview",
          "title": "Fall Themes",
          "content": "# Fall Themes\n\nA collection of five autumn-inspired color themes for Clubhouse.\n\n## Themes\n\n### Maple (Light)\nRich reds and burnt oranges on warm cream — the bold, fiery palette of maple leaves at peak color.\n\n### Harvest (Light)\nEarthy wheat and warm browns. A rustic, grounded theme inspired by golden fields and harvest baskets.\n\n### Pumpkin Spice (Light)\nWarm orange and cinnamon tones. A cozy, inviting palette that wraps your editor in autumn warmth.\n\n### Amber Forest (Light)\nGolden amber light filtering through a forest canopy. Warm yellows meet deep greens on a sunny fall afternoon.\n\n### Twilight Ember (Dark)\nGlowing embers against a dusky sky. Deep, warm darks with vivid orange and coral accents, like the last light of an autumn bonfire.\n\n## Usage\n\nInstall the plugin and select any Fall Theme from **Settings > Appearance > Theme**."
        }
      ]
